 arch/x86/Kconfig                              |  9 -------
 arch/x86/include/asm/pgalloc.h                |  5 ----
 arch/x86/mm/pgtable.c                         | 27 +------------------
 4 files changed, 1 insertion(+), 47 deletions(-)

